# Probe output -- by default keep local runs out of git; explicitly commit
# reference runs (e.g. the demo-layer validation) via `git add -f`.
# The TEMPLATE and any files named schema-ground-truth-reference-*.md are
# always tracked.
docs/schema-ground-truth-20*.md
!docs/schema-ground-truth-TEMPLATE.md
!docs/schema-ground-truth-reference-*.md

